This is Easy Guideline For Everyone To install the Program for Free.

Step 1: After you download program of this file in your device

    -Open this folder by use your IDE Program eg. VSCode ,AntiGravity ,and etc.
    -After you open your IDE. Check that you has *all the important file we need*
        -filename 
        database.js 
        ,index.html 
        ,main.js 
        ,package.json 
        ,package-lock.json 
        ,preload.js 
        ,renderer.js 
        ,start.js 
        ,Style.css

Step 2: After you got all the file. run this in your terminal.
        
        npm install
        
    -this should download need packages for this project. 

Step 3: Check that everything is ready to build

    -Run this command to Test the program.

        npm start

    -Then you will found App that OpenUp
    -Check if there was no any bugs

Step 4: Build Program for Real use

    -Run this command to starting build a program

        npm run build:portable

    -this should start building portable app
    -App size is Around 500Mb for all module

Step 5: Check your App

    -App that had builded should be in folder

        dist/

    -you will found a App Name 
        
        Novel Manager 1.x.0.exe

    -Open the app to check that App was builded Correctly

Step last: And done

    -You can move the folder Dist/ into The folder you want and changed into name you want.
